        <item>
            <title>【評測】NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92   三頻 WiFi 6E Mesh + 提升隔牆上網速度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:45:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[路由器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETGEAR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wi-Fi 6E]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1228536</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著科技發展，即使安坐家中，相信大家都會手執電話、手提電腦、遊戲機、平板等多部裝置連接網絡，如用家需要欣賞 4K HDR 影片、Hi-Res 音樂等，對頻寬要求只會有增無減，對網絡連接的需求亦相應提高。若你需要更快更穩定的網絡連接設備，就要考慮購置 Wi-Fi 6E Mesh Wi-Fi 裝置。今次我們會實測 NETGEAR 近日推出的 Nighthawk 系列最新產品：MK92 Mesh Wi-Fi 6 路由器，看看它如何解決上網死角問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09434.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MK72S 是一款高速三頻 Wi-Fi 6 Mesh System，其 5GHz 及 6GHz Wi-Fi 頻道可支援 160MHz 頻道，令無線傳輸可媲美傳統有線傳輸，而且表現比同級數其他產品更為優秀及穏定。全新四核心 1.7 GHz 的處理器比以往的型號支援更多裝置同時上網，即使是多裝置使用的重度網絡使用者都十分適合。</p><h2>頂部浮雕設計，盒狀機身融入家居</h2><p>今次評測的 NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92 外觀設計簡約，機頂設計是簡單大方的網格狀正方立體浮雕，簡約之餘亦不失細緻。</p><p>包裝內有一個主路由器和一個衞星子機。Nighhawk MK92 機身四正，放在家中不會突兀。而今次外殼使用的材料是高反光鋼琴麪塑膠，質感滿滿，惟一要批評的是捉摸後容易留下指紋。整個機身設計四正，佔地不多，適合在家居任何位置安裝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09423.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09429.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機頂立方體浮雕設計感覺時尚</p><h2>機身接口多，按需求連接</h2><p>Nighthawk MK92 的路由器 MK92 主機提供 1 個 2.5Gig 網際網路埠及 3 個以太網埠，分機亦提供 2 個以太網埠，讓用家可以連接遊戲機、電腦、IoT 設備等裝置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09428.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器主機提供 2.5Gig 網際網路埠及 3 個以太網埠</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc09426.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器主機（上）；衞星分機（下）提供 2 個以太網埠</p><p>&nbsp;<br /><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-nighthawk-mk92/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全新 WiFi 6E Mesh 系統   Nighthawk MK92 三頻 WiFi 適合高達 5,000 呎環境</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-april-sale/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 四月優惠推介  2.5G WAN、WiFi 6E、WiFi 7 路由器出機優惠</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/netgear-wifi-6e-product-sale-2024-spring/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全線 WiFi 6E 產品特價，初春優惠推介</a></li></blockquote><p></p><h2>安裝方便，一個 App 即可完成設定</h2><p>用家只需要插上電源線，其後連接 LAN 線和主機，就能夠完成主路由器最初硬件設置。而主機初始設定亦簡易明瞭。為顧及新手，Netgear 推出了 Nighthawk 專用應用程式，替主路由器和衞星子機連接電源並開機後，下載 NETGEAR Nighthawk 手機 App ，申請 Netgear 帳戶後，只要掃描路由器的 QR Code，其後的手續就可交由應用程式自動設置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載「NETGEAR Nighthawk」應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲註冊「NETGEAR」帳戶</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲註冊「NETGEAR」帳戶</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇你的產品，小編手上的是 Nighthawk Mesh 系統</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279872.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲掃描路由器底部的 QR Code</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 應用程式會自動替你完成剩下的步驟</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228798" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279911.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此時需要按「加入」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279912.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279913.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Nighthawk 應用程式會自動替你掃描衞星子機</p><p style="text-align: left;">等手機連接到路由器和衞星子機便可直接上網了。用戶事後如果想調整任何設定，亦可利用 Nighthawk 手機 App 遙距管理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228801" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712828807.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看見這個頁面就代表已經完成掃描所有衞星子機</p><h2>網速測試</h2><p>MK90 是三頻 Mesh Wi-Fi 6E 裝置，能夠連接更多裝置，覆蓋範圍和網絡表現更佳。我們在辦公室進行實際測試，嘗試在複雜環境下如何解決無線網絡訊號問題。使用 Netgear Nighthawk 應用程式內置的網絡測速功能可得出下載 2314.30 Mbps、上傳 965.72 Mbps 和 9ms 延遲的測試結果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/787e0e11b6e44c83a52a.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 應用程式內置的網絡測速功能</p><p>首先我們在路由器 2 米範圍內，Samsung S24 Ultra 手機裝上「Speedtest」網絡測速軟件測得下載 1,901 Mbps，上載 1,207 Mbps，延遲 5 ms。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-scaled.jpg 455w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲離路由器 2 米（沒有牆壁阻隔）</p><p>小編在沒有牆壁阻隔的情況下，Samsung S24 Ultra 手機距離路由器約 5 米再使用測速軟件，測得下載 1,574 Mbps，上載 1,158 Mbps，延遲仍能夠保持在 5 ms。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229419" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-2-scaled.jpg 455w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲離路由器 5 米的測試結果（沒有牆壁阻隔）</p><p>小編這次在隔住一面牆，Samsung S24 Ultra 手機遠離路由器 10 米的情況下使用測速軟件，下載錄得 1,002 Mbps，上載 770 Mbps，延遲只稍為提升至 9 ms，即使隔住一面牆，表現仍然令人滿意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-293x580.jpg" alt="" width="293" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-293x580.jpg 293w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot_20240415_-1-scaled.jpg 454w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 293px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲離路由器 10 米的測試結果（中間有一面牆）</p><h2>總結：安裝無困難 覆蓋範圍廣</h2><p>Nighthawk MK92 安裝非常簡單便捷，即使是電腦新手亦能輕鬆自行安裝。實際試用時，可見衞星子機能改善隔牆上網體驗，最重要的是新增衞星子機亦非常輕鬆，全程可以用 App 直接自動設置。<br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-nighthawk-mk92/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全新 WiFi 6E Mesh 系統   Nighthawk MK92 三頻 WiFi 適合高達 5,000 呎環境</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/05/netgear-april-sale/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 四月優惠推介  2.5G WAN、WiFi 6E、WiFi 7 路由器出機優惠</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/netgear-wifi-6e-product-sale-2024-spring/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 全線 WiFi 6E 產品特價，初春優惠推介</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/netgear-nighthawk-mk92-2/wireless-home/routers/">【評測】NETGEAR Nighthawk MK92   三頻 WiFi 6E Mesh + 提升隔牆上網速度</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
